<C>__{athos}
<D>__{i am not... i am not angry with you. you understand? good. now, as to acting like a king, we wish you to be a good king. but at first... at first you must pass as louis, and louis is cold and cruel. so you must stop looking at people with such softness. it is... not kingly. the eyes of a king say that all he cares about is himself, and your eyes how do i tell him this ? you eyes... ask so much. you shouldn't care about me, about my about...}
